Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:37.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:55.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:23.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:28.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:33.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:34.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:37.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:47.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:55.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:00.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:23.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:26.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:33.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:44.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力收监设施受Gundam袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事的确属实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是天人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有传闻说反政府组织独立开发了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些纯属臆测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 这都是威胁现任政权的恐怖行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府为了消灭恐怖组织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已决定派遣直属治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预见到天人的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来利用之扩大A-LAWS的权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的想法 还是Veda的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 差不多轮到我们出场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里维夫·里维尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gadessa也已下线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要下令立刻就能出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有必要 里维夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个作战我已拜托某人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪万吗 还是布林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然某种意义上超越人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:54.54,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(525,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}故国燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 留守太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特莱玛奥斯的修补
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS新型MS的检验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Twin Drive系统的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事多着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是好烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(354,367)}鲁布哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:16.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（阿拉伯半岛南部大沙漠，东部是石油产地）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没被联邦发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦在非加盟国众多的中东全域都散布了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上是为了用粒子效果屏蔽恐怖组织的情报网
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际目的是麻痹中东国家的经济活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遵从联邦政策的国家都会遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多亏GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的设施才没被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是常识范畴内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗 已确认你们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 救了阿撒迪斯坦的英雄机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得好啊 天人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一睹尊容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有保密义务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么死板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟受了恩惠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织 KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们接受会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是KATARON中东支部的克劳斯·格拉多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是天人 自我介绍就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你们的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们救了玛莉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们会负责保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想待在天人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 怎会在反政府组织里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人想拜托你们保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德 是平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被A-LAWS怀疑是KATARON成员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你真是受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会负责保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 怎么擅自就
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么能随便进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把他们作为KATARON成员来培养吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为无依无靠的孩子们提供保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦单方面的中东政策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是其实际损害的一种表现形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过由于资金有限 不可能收容所有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是玛莉娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你是玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔殿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也认识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的是玛莉娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜殿下 能麻烦你陪陪孩子们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 那这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是国家的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该进入正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们KATARON是为了打倒现任联邦政权…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 我们并非和你们一样是遵循政治思想而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们和联邦对立
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人不是联邦政府 而是A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐政府直辖独立部队不是和我们目的一致吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制裁A-LAWS的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也应携手共进…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的MS是对付不了GN Drive搭载型机的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想协助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是补给和整备方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想助你们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(354,367)}波斯湾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然损失了Trilobite 真失态啊 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在没脸见人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛内金上校 你与少校共同指挥部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们A-LAWS既是联邦的矛也是联邦的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不容许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 今后也请遵从我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧 Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有司令部批准的独立行动许可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是One Man Army
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我有许可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校您出动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探索Gundam部队的活交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军居然要给A-LAWS打杂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 他还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说安德烈少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在忠实执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在讽刺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怨恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽是个军人 却不配为人父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 那件事…我打算接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做上校养女的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情见面再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜殿下 这个也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你们的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们所改变的世界的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就毫无感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也无法进入那个圈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道 为何还要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没打算得到你的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 请听我一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要拉拢天人很困难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有那个回答就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和A-LAWS的战斗将愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之后 他们就会和我们携手共进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 Gin-1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还要摸鱼到几时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回自己岗位干活去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会谈结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但现在有件事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要做?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔送去阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被发现 可能会殃及阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用这个机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把Gundam运回托勒密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 不回来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四年间出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人和KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是引发战争的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是天人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在城里有同伴 想联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城里太远 开车去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到玛莉娜公主了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还和天人的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要回母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他们出动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能穿越沙漠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在荒漠中驾驶轻吉普兜风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生化测量器有反应 这人是KATARON成员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 我来审问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是战士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长年在军中我能看出 你没有战斗者的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说 你不是KATARON的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否和天人一起行动?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从资料看几周前你还在Gundam出现的PROUD从事殖民卫星开发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你又出现在这片与Gundam发生战事的地域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什么 简单的推理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不是KATARON也不是天人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 只希望如实告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会为难你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能洗刷我的嫌疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会斟酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四宇航队 巴拉克·吉宁上尉以下五人前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 情报确实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个心软的女人容易错失良机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好消息 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了KATARON的军事基地 Gundam也很可能在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即应对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 请允许我们也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强 先养精蓄锐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam明明就在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这命令是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启用自动机器人的歼灭模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁想出这种非人道的作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 上层的命令必须绝对服从
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这纸命令的内容毫无想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没有 对方是反政府势力 何必手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种作战…终于明白上校反对这次调配的原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史米卢佐夫上校为完成任务不惜牺牲亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人对母亲见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 A-LAWS掌握了反政府组织的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会联系提耶利亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你报告给A-LAWS了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出判断的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库斯洛德 马上离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS得知了你的存在 他们是法外部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的权限无法保证你安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道我的存在 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颜色是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发来紧急暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS队正朝KATARON的基地去 怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往救援 托勒密启动对卫星光学迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急上浮 布置Gundam准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 开始紧急上浮  距离海面0043
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS发现了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…给我再快些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS的MS队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来攻击这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里泄露了基地的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是天人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快带孩子去防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 主动出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战力差距悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严防死守 等待天人支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌人基地设施
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌方MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那么旧型的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始扫荡敌人基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人 射出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军用自动机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了一步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯机 迎击先行的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 迎击Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴味索然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这还有没有人性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人兵器的虐杀行径
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亲手扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用承担负罪感了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双联火箭炮 轰击模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初期目标完成 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 饶不了你们 A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃啊 别逃啊 A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那就是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵 为战斗而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也想获得常人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是报应吗 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都因为…我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的
