Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿撒迪斯坦会…为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这规模…不是恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那涂装…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一样都揪动着人心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 伤痕
